snippet.title: Goldie (Dingo Pictures Remaster)
snippet.description:
I'll be honest. I think this might be one of the better Dingo Pictures films, if only for the narrator. He just has this soothing voice that's almost ASMR-like. If this didn't have visuals, it would make for a nice little audio book. Anyways, there's only one English version of Goldie here on YouTube, and that's a direct rip from the Midas Interactive PS1 port. So I made another Phelous-styled Frankenstein's monster and synced the English audio to a Finnish version also on YouTube.

#DingoPictures #UnintentionalASMR
